---
group_count: 17
atr1_unknown: 0
entries:
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk000:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 284
      - text: "你這傢伙真是個了不起的伯伊，\n烏爾波扎的憤怒用起來應該也比以往更熟練了吧。"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk010:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 273
      - text: "小公主……就要麻煩你多費心了。\n畢竟我託付的，可是海拉魯引以為傲的勇者喔。"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk100:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 216
      - text: "海拉魯的勇者依然健在啊，\n本領還是一樣高強。"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk110:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 284
      - text: "但你可不能大意喔，\n我們都不想再見到小公主的眼淚，對吧？"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk200:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 153
      - text: "我見識到了喔，\n真是漂亮的劍術。"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk210:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 234
      - text: "話說，你去過格魯德小鎮了吧？\n現在是誰擔任族長？"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk220:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 246
      - text: "100年前我遭逢不測……\n大家應該都過得很煎熬。"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk230:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 336
      - text: "但我相信……格魯德是強悍的民族，\n無論遇到什麼災難，人民都能挺身面對！"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk300:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 177
      - text: "你又來了啊？\n哎呀，你一定沒問題的。"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk310:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 146
      - text: 我倒是有件事想問問你……
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk320:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 186
      - text: "之前你去格魯德小鎮的時候，\n是怎麼混進去的？"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk330:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 232
      - text: 難不成……你又打扮成那副模樣了？
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk340:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 241
      - text: "那套衣服100年前也很適合你呢，\n我都想讓小公主開開眼界了。"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk400:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 195
      - text: "我都看見了喔。\n我已經沒什麼事要交代你了。"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk410:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 186
      - text: "啊，對了對了，\n如果你在哪裡發現我的日記……"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk420:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 230
      - text: "找個機會讓小公主看看吧。\n因為裡頭也記錄了我的朋友……"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk430:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 332
      - text: "也就是她母親的點點滴滴。\n她留下女兒，早早便辭世了。"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk440:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 112
      - text: 心裡想必有許多遺憾吧……
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk500:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 246
      - text: "結果我還是拜託了你一堆事。\n小公主的事，還有海拉魯的事……"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk510:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 264
      - text: "你一定能辦到的……\n畢竟你是我所認識最優秀的伯伊。"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk520:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 220
      - text: "等打倒加儂之後，\n我會帶著小公主的話題當作伴手禮……"
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk530:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 101
      - text: 給她的母親……
  Npc_Gerudo_Hero_talk540:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 262
      - text: "我會告訴她，「公主殿下身邊有一位\n出色的騎士，所以什麼都不必擔心」。"
